metadata.name: Frida Kahlo's Rebirth as a Pharaoh #1/1
metadata.description:
"The NFT titled "Frida Kahlo's Rebirth as a Pharaoh" is a unique and rare work of art. The piece is a perfect combination of Frida's creativity and mystic side. This work, in which Frida blends her own style with Egyptian mythology, offers a captivating visual experience.
Frida Kahlo's art has always been inspiring. By turning her own painful experiences into a message through her art, she has created an inspiring impact on people's ability to live and fight.

Come, let's embark on a mystical journey with Frida!"

By Enes Sagdic
